<article elid="2629985353" class="clearfix image-article sm-mb-1 quality-HD post-2629985353" >
    <div class="row px10">
        <div id="col-center" class="col sm-mb-1" style="width:100.0%;"><div class="widget__body clearfix sm-mt-1"><div class="headline-container">
    <h1 class="headline h1">
        A map of Kim Jong-un’s slow train trip to Vietnam
    </h1>
</div>
<div class="widget__subheadline">
    <h2 class="widget__subheadline-text h2"><p>North Korea's Great Leader would rather not fly for his second summit with Trump – but the trip is also a political message to China.</p></h2>
</div>
<div class="post-author-list"><div class="post-author">
            <a href="https://bigthink.com/u/frankjacobs">
                
