<h2 class="widget__headline h2">
    <a class="widget__headline-text custom-post-headline" href="https://bigthink.com/Charles-Koch-Foundation/big-picture-learning"  aria-label="Our schools are built differently. That’s how we’re weathering this pandemic.">
        Our schools are built differently. That’s how we’re weathering this pandemic.
    </a>
</h2>
<div class="widget__subheadline">
    <h3 class="widget__subheadline-text h3"><p>'Know thy students' is the principle that can change the form of education, worldwide.</p></h3>
</div>


<div class="social-author clearfix">
    

    
        
    <div class="social-author__avatar image" >
             
             <div class="cover-all image" style='background-image: url("https://assets.rebelmouse.io/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpbWFnZSI6Imh0dHBzOi8vYXNzZXRzLnJibC5tcy8yMzI4MzAwNi9vcmlnaW4uanBnIiwiZXhwaXJlc19hdCI6MTYzOTgwODk4MH0.-j_TlbEKeHTCjihNYTT4YvECyYO4f2_rOEsidnNKpYk/img.jpg?width=210")'></div>
             
        </div>
        <a class="social-author__name" href="https://bigthink.com/u/elliotwashor">Elliot Washor</a>
        
</div>
<div class="social-date">
        <span class="social-date__text">15 May, 2020</span>
    </div></div><div class="widget__head"><a href="https://bigthink.com/Charles-Koch-Foundation/big-picture-learning"  aria-label="Our schools are built differently. That’s how we’re weathering this pandemic.">
                            
