<h2 class="widget__headline h2">
    <a class="widget__headline-text custom-post-headline" href="https://bigthink.com/surprising-science/china-moon-cotton"  aria-label="China grew a plant on the moon — it sprouted two leaves, data indicates">
        China grew a plant on the moon — it sprouted two leaves, data indicates
    </a>
</h2>
<div class="widget__subheadline">
    <h3 class="widget__subheadline-text h3"><p>It marks the first time a plant has been grown on the moon.</p></h3>
</div>


