    <div class="row px10">
        <div id="col-center" class="col sm-mb-1" style="width:100.0%;"><div class="widget__body clearfix sm-mt-1">
<h2 class="widget__headline h2">
    <a class="widget__headline-text custom-post-headline" href="https://bigthink.com/surprising-science/obesity-antidepressants"  aria-label="Weight gain affects the efficacy of antidepressants, new study finds">
        Weight gain affects the efficacy of antidepressants, new study finds
    </a>
</h2>
<div class="widget__subheadline">
    <h3 class="widget__subheadline-text h3"><p>Weight gain is a side effect of antidepressants, adding another layer of problems. </p></h3>
</div>


<div class="social-author clearfix">
    

    
        
    <div class="social-author__avatar image" >
             
             <div class="cover-all image" style='background-image: url("https://assets.rebelmouse.io/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpbWFnZSI6Imh0dHBzOi8vYXNzZXRzLnJibC5tcy8xODQwMTYyOC9vcmlnaW4uanBnIiwiZXhwaXJlc19hdCI6MTYxMzcwNTc2Nn0.iVQyxN8HA7avJDwCDF4hlwepGncgIlUhRB4_iTCLI6c/img.jpg?width=210")'></div>
             
        </div>
        <a class="social-author__name" href="https://bigthink.com/u/derek-beres">Derek Beres</a>
        
</div>
<div class="social-date">
        <span class="social-date__text">23 June, 2020</span>
    </div></div><div class="widget__head"><a href="https://bigthink.com/surprising-science/obesity-antidepressants"  aria-label="Weight gain affects the efficacy of antidepressants, new study finds">
                            
