<h2 class="widget__headline h2">
    <a class="widget__headline-text custom-post-headline" href="https://bigthink.com/surprising-science/particle-accelerator"  aria-label="Why we can stop worrying and love the particle accelerator">
        Why we can stop worrying and love the particle accelerator
    </a>
</h2>
<div class="widget__subheadline">
    <h3 class="widget__subheadline-text h3"><p>By delving into the mysteries of the Universe, colliders have entered the Zeitgeist and tapped the wonders and fears of our age.</p></h3>
</div>


